" $ sudo -u www vi ~www/htdocs/index.html\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
" $ sudo -u www vi ~www/htdocs/index.html\n"
"\n"

#. type: textblock
#: C/sudo.pod:730
msgid "To view system logs only accessible to root and users in the adm group:"
